</p><p>BJCVS believes it is on the right track by prioritizing the quality of its publications
and a structure that protects the authenticity of published work, what is reflected in
the journal indicators.</p><sec><title>Articles in this Issue</title><p>This issue of BJCVS presents a blind peer-reviewed selection of 20 papers that were
