case reports and 1 letter to the editor.</p></sec><sig-block><bold>Paulo Roberto B. Evora</bold><break/> https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9631-946X<break/><sup>1</sup>Editor-in-Chief Interim - BJCVS<break/> Faculdade de Medicina de
